Module org.firebirdsql.jaybird
Package org.firebirdsql.gds

Interface ISCConstants

public interface ISCConstants
Constants for Firebird features, parameter blocks and errors.

Some constants previously held in this interface have been moved to:

  • DpbItems
  • SpbItems
  • TpbItems
  • BpbItems
  • BpbItems.TypeValues

Author:
Alejandro Alberola, David Jencks
